Impulse Boots	KEY:Incarnate Soulmeld ~ Impulse Boots	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Soulmeld.ChakraFeet.Incarnate.IncarnateChakraFeet	SOURCEPAGE:p.71	ASPECT:Chakra|Feet	DESC:You shape incarnum into boots that surround your feet (as well as any other footwear you might have) and reach up almost to your knees. Midnight blue in color, the impulse boots seem to be made of smooth, supple leather. You channel the spirits of rogues and scoundrels, barbarians, and all who think quickly on their feet, forming that elemental quality into boots that help you do the same. Your impulse boots grant you the ability to avoid dangerous effects. While wearing this soulmeld, you gain the uncanny dodge ability (see page 50 of the Player's Handbook). Essentia: You gain an enhancement bonus on Reflex saves equal to the number of points of essentia invested.	DESC:Chakra Bind (Feet) Your impulse boots merge with your feet, and extend their midnight- blue color in tendrils reaching up your legs to your waist, like snaking veins just under your skin. You gain the evasion ability (see page 50 of the Player's Handbook).
