Silvertongue Mask (Throat)	KEY:Incarnate Soulmeld ~ Silvertongue Mask (Throat)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	DESC:Chakra Bind (Throat) The silver mask melds into your face and neck, from your cheekbones down to your collar, as if your skin were turned to silver. When you attempt to compel a creature, that creature sees a face that is recognizable, but not quite familiar. When bound to the throat chakra, the silvertongue mask allows you to make a suggestion (as the spell) to any creature as a standard action. A successful Will save negates this effect. A creature targeted by this ability, regardless of whether or not it succeeds on its save, can't be targeted again by the same ability for 24 hours. This is a mind-affecting, languagedependent effect.	TYPE:IncarnateSoulmeldApplied.Amulet	BONUS:SLOTS|Neck|-1	SOURCEPAGE:p.86	BONUS:VAR|ChakraBindThroat|1	PREVARLT:ChakraBindThroat,1	BONUS:VAR|IncarnateChakraBindThroat|-1	PREVARGTEQ:IncarnateChakraBindThroat,1	BONUS:VAR|IncarnateSoulmeldApplied|1	PREVARLT:IncarnateSoulmeldsCount,IncarnateSoulmeldApplied
