Blink Shirt
	KEY:Totemist Soulmeld ~ Blink Shirt
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:Soulmeld.ChakraHeart.ChakraTotem.Totemist.TotemistChakraXyX
	DESC:This rough-looking garment fits over armor and other clothing and looks like it has been made of coarse brown fur, but it displays obviously magical features. The shirt seems to shift and move on its own, and it fades into a barely corporeal mist near your waist. Most disconcerting of all, patches of the garment seem transparent, as if they have temporarily shifted to some strange elsewhere. Because different parts of the garment appear phased out at different times, these patches of incorporeality seem to roam over the surface of the shirt. Blink dogs have two closely related abilities that define their hunting tactics. Totemists emulate both their shortrange teleportation and the blinking that gives them their name. Good-aligned totemists and those planning to fight displacer beasts shape this meld, invoking the blink dog's natural good alignment and their hatred for those creatures. By shaping incarnum into a shirt resembling blink dog fur, you gain the ability to teleport (as dimension door) up to 10 feet at will. Using this ability is a standard action. After using this ability, you can't take any other actions until your next turn. You cannot bring along other creatures; you affect only yourself. Essentia: Investing essentia in this soulmeld increases the distance you can teleport. For every point of essentia invested, you can teleport an additional 10 feet.
	DESC:Chakra Bind (Heart) The appearance of your blink shirt changes little, except that now wherever it seems transparent, you do as well. Strange patches of incorporeality float over your entire body. You can use blink as the spell (with a caster level equal to your meldshaper level). Activating or dismissing the effect is a standard action.
	DESC:Chakra Bind (Totem) Your posture becomes slightly hunched, giving you the merest hint of a canine appearance. Your ears also take on sharp points. You can use the dimension door ability of this soulmeld as a move action.
